{"tid":121963,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"老實講 巴打如果自己係女 唔會要求男人有錢啲咩？","createTime":"2017-02-15T15:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T03:47:58.000Z","uid":46400,"like":58,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1d14a9d4b46433a4de93b150cc52ebb82eb2e4b7","tid":121963,"uid":46400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T15:45:46.000Z","msg":"如果你係女，仲要靚靚地識打扮咁，本身就算咩都唔做，日常出街都已經有機會比人聊，根本大把選擇，有咩理由要簡一個又唔靚仔又無身型既窮撚？<br />\n<br />\n你話有錢靚仔肯定唔專一好仆街，一黎就話咩中出即飛，唔會認真。但事實上人地分分中每一樣野都比你好，你講到人地一定有啲缺點係因為你本身無一樣野好先會覺得自己可以對人好好，係真愛，而你所謂對人好其實只係其他人既一少部分。<br />\n<br />\n有時真係將心比己啦，唔好成日溝唔到女就話人係雞啦（當然其實有部分真係雞）<br />\n<br />\n利申：窮毒撚"},{"pid":"769a5d5ce47e17902ffd08557099cd6c05c141b1","tid":121963,"uid":46400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T15:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a10b667f4d359668a7667bfd257bbd7e1adcb2","tid":121963,"uid":46400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T15:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"addc5078f3a1e8a2bb8404ecfbfebbc4830eb818","tid":121963,"uid":46400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T15:55:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237499e733b973e6596e6eabfb5dcf0a27f8a3e4","tid":121963,"uid":46400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"h